(* ============================================================================
   格点QCD中核子非极化胶子TMD部分子分布函数的完整推导
   使用梯度流重整化方案的连续极限计算

   Lattice QCD Calculation of the Unpolarized Gluon TMD PDF
   of the Nucleon in the Continuum Limit
   Using Gradient Flow Renormalization

   基于本库全部文档与代码的综合推导
   Based on comprehensive derivation from all documents and code in this repository

   参考文献 (References):
   - Chen et al. (CLQCD/LPC), "Unpolarized gluon PDF of the nucleon
     from lattice QCD in the continuum limit", arXiv:2510.26425 (2025)
   - He et al. (LPC), "Unpolarized TMD parton distributions of the nucleon
     from lattice QCD", PRD 109, 114513 (2024)
   - Zhang et al. (LPC), "Renormalization of TMD parton distribution
     on the lattice", PRD 106, 094510 (2022)
   - Balitsky, Morris, Radyushkin, "Gluon pseudo-distributions at short
     distances: Forward case", PLB 808, 135621 (2020)
   - Ji, "Parton physics on a Euclidean lattice", PRL 110, 262002 (2013)
   - Luescher, "Properties and uses of the Wilson flow in lattice QCD",
     JHEP 08, 071 (2010)
   - Monahan & Orginos, "Quasi parton distributions and the gradient flow",
     JHEP 03, 116 (2017)
   - Izubuchi et al., "Factorization theorem relating Euclidean and
     light-cone parton distributions", PRD 98, 056004 (2018)
   - Li, Ma, Qiu, "Multiplicative renormalizability of quasi-parton operators",
     PRL 122, 062002 (2019)
   - Zhang, Ji, Schaefer, Wang, Zhao, "Accessing gluon parton distributions
     in LaMET", PRL 122, 142001 (2019)
   ============================================================================ *)

(* 加载所有子模块 *)
Get[FileNameJoin[{NotebookDirectory[], "01_FieldStrengthTensor.m"}]];
Get[FileNameJoin[{NotebookDirectory[], "02_GradientFlow.m"}]];
Get[FileNameJoin[{NotebookDirectory[], "03_GluonQuasiTMD_Operator.m"}]];
Get[FileNameJoin[{NotebookDirectory[], "04_StapleWilsonLine.m"}]];
Get[FileNameJoin[{NotebookDirectory[], "05_Renormalization.m"}]];
Get[FileNameJoin[{NotebookDirectory[], "06_LaMET_Factorization.m"}]];
Get[FileNameJoin[{NotebookDirectory[], "07_ContinuumExtrapolation.m"}]];
